cs.RO, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.SY, cs.CV 

Reasoning: 
- cs.RO (Robotics) is the most likely category as the paper presents a method for an autonomous marine vehicle to perform persistent ocean monitoring tasks. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is also likely as the paper proposes a planning and learning method for the vehicle to learn and refine an environmental model. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is relevant as the paper uses sparse Gaussian Process learning to learn the environmental model. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is relevant as the paper deals with controlling an autonomous marine vehicle for environmental monitoring. 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) is less likely but still possible as the paper may involve image processing for ocean monitoring.
